<p>The <b>Huguenots</b> were members of the <a href="/wiki/Protestantism" title="Protestantism">Protestant</a> <a href="/wiki/Reformed_Church_of_France" title="Reformed Church of France">Reformed Church</a> of <a href="/wiki/France" title="France">France</a> (or French <a href="/wiki/Calvinism" title="Calvinism">Calvinists</a>) from the sixteenth to the eighteenth centuries.</p>
